  - Quantile-Tree: fits many quantile models and is conservatively capped at n=100,000
  - Quantile-Linear: disabled above n=10,000 by the linear-quantile baseline itself
  - BART-Homo: XBART baselines are conservatively capped at n=100,000 for this scaling study
  - BART-Hetero: XBART baselines are conservatively capped at n=100,000 for this scaling study

